    <p>So you want to help us? That's pretty awesome!<br>
    We are very happy to accept external contributions in the form of feedback, bug reports or pull requests :)</p>
    <p>Feel free to help on one of these two primary repos:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloy-ui/">AlloyUI Library</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloyui.com/">AlloyUI Website</a></li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="title span12">
        <h3>website</h3>
        <p>help!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>For now, you can help us with the website by writing tutorials or examples for the components that we haven't added yet. <a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloyui.com/wiki/List-of-Components">See the list of components that need to be added</a>.</p>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloyui.com/wiki/How-to-create-a-new-tutorial">How to create a new tutorial</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloyui.com/wiki/How-to-create-a-new-example">How to create a new example</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p><strong>Remember:</strong> Before any pull request don't forget to run: <code>ant jshint</code>. If you find any error please fix it before sending your pull request.</p>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="title span12">
        <h3>issues</h3>
        <p>github or jira?</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>First of all, you should know that we're not using the <a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloy-ui/issues">Github Issues</a>, instead we use <a href="http://issues.liferay.com/browse/AUI">Jira</a>.<br>
    In order for us to help you please check that you've completed the following steps:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><p>Make sure that you're using the latest version.</p></li>
      <li><p>Look through the list of issues to ensure that the bug hasn't been reported before.</p></li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you're still facing the problem, go ahead and <a href="http://issues.liferay.com/secure/CreateIssue!default.jspa">create an issue</a>.<br>
    Just remember to include as much information about the bug as possible.</p>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="title span12">
        <h3>style guide</h3>
        <p>tabs or spaces?</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>This project uses single-quotes, two space indentation, multiple var statements and whitespace around arguments. Please ensure any pull requests follow this closely by using the <a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloyui.com/blob/master/.editorconfig">EditorConfig file</a> and linting your code with our <a href="https://github.com/liferay/alloyui.com/blob/master/.jshintrc">JSHint options</a>. If you notice existing code which doesn't follow these practices, feel free to shout out and we will change it.</p>

    <p>Also, remember to sort configuration attributes in a logical order:</p>

    <ol>
      <li>DOM manipulation</li>
      <li>Specific module logics in alphabetical order</li>
      <li>Style configurations</li>
    </ol>
    <p>For example:</p>

    <pre><code class="javascript">new A.Carousel({
    contentBox: '#demo', // 1. DOM manipulation
    activeIndex: 'rand', // 2. Specific module logics in alphabetical order
    intervalTime: 2, // 2. Specific module logics in alphabetical order
    width: 680, // 3. Style configurations
    height: 254 // 3. Style configurations
}).render();</code></pre>

